    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/58b6a6c5967f9435207e0a36198ba03a.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/58b6a6c5967f9435207e0a36198ba03a.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/58b6a6c5967f9435207e0a36198ba03a.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ 探索</strong></h2> 隐藏着<strong>秘密区域</strong>和<strong>谜题</strong>与<strong>陷阱[/一样多的外星世界的遗迹b] 和 <strong> 鬼鬼祟祟的生物</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/fdc38c80de8d60e19a3d780b4b5ff1e8.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/fdc38c80de8d60e19a3d780b4b5ff1e8.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/fdc38c80de8d60e19a3d780b4b5ff1e8.mp4?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ♱ 狡猾 </strong></h2> 巧妙地使用你的物品来战斗和解决难题。使用景观元素来<strong>隐藏</strong>和<strong>一次性生物</strong>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/646bb17a60ed49265d8281d57d2c6095.poster.avif?t=1690397332\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857780/extras/646bb17a60ed49265d8281d57d2c6095.webm?t=1690397332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/